data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom, 2 full bath home only 7 years old in the highly desired neighborhood of Briar Oaks. This home features wood kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. A large master bedroom suite with a walk-in shower, dual sinks with granite stone tops and a walk-in closet. The sliding glass door from the living room opens to a covered lanai. Beautiful vinyl fencing gives you the privacy you need and great for pets as it is completely fenced in. There are not many 4 bedrooms homes with 1500+ of living sq footage in this condition. A home that is less than 10 years old. It is an amazing opportunity for a first-time home buyer or someone looking to make this their home for a long time. More photos coming soon!!!
